Trend Hunter features user generated content and submissions made from independent parties around the world. The primary purpose of our website is for research.  
We study the interactions with images representing ideas to better understand and predict consumer changes. 
<BR>
<BR>
Because of our research methodology, we require thousands of experiments and articles to have enough data to detect trends with statistically significant assurance.  At any given time there are thousands of experiments on the active portion of the site. 
